      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hermes is the local control plane: it listens across channels, reasons with provider models, remembers through Honcho, edits notes/code through tools, controls Hue lamps, and delegates implementation to Cursor or Codex when needed.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "originalText": "Hermes is the local control plane: it listens across channels, reasons with provider models, remembers through Honcho, edits notes/code through tools, controls Hue lamps, and delegates implementation to Cursor or Codex when needed.",
